### Note on GenomeScope visualization

GenomeScope can be run locally (as done in this pipeline) or via the
GenomeScope web interface:

https://genomescope.org/

The web interface is used **for visualization and exploratory inspection only**.
All quantitative results reported in this repository (genome size,
heterozygosity, repeat content, error rate, and model fit) are generated from
the **local GenomeScope 2.0 command-line runs** to ensure full reproducibility.

The web interface does not replace the local analysis and should not be treated
as an independent computational step.
